### 6. Assistant Webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/assistant-chat
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "query": "Necesito ayuda con mi cuenta",
  "assistantId": "asst_123456"
}

### 7. File Upload Analysis (Test 1: PDF/Text)
POST {{baseUrl}}/openai-chat
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="idUserChat"

user_test_concatenation
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento1.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Contenido del primer documento.
--boundary--

### 8. File Upload Analysis (Test 2: Image/PDF - Ver Concat)
POST {{baseUrl}}/openai-chat
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="idUserChat"

user_test_concatenation
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento2.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Contenido del segundo documento que se debe concatenar.
--boundary--
